snippet.title: Mushroom 11 - Available Now!
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam, GOG and Humble Store on October 15th 2015, National Mushroom Day!

Steam: http://bit.ly/1jqr4qw
GOG: http://bit.ly/1RK04NT
Humble: http://bit.ly/1RcE9Oz

In Mushroom 11 you are an amorphous fungal organism spared by the catastrophe that wiped out the human race. Shape your mushroom by pruning its cells. New cells immediately grow to replace the ones destroyed, allowing you to move through and explore a mysterious world where the total annihilation of humanity has cleared the way for unexpected new life.

Music by The Future Sound of London.

Website: http://mushroom11.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/untamegames
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mushroom11
